  * d/p/clang-fix-cmpxchg8-detection-on-i386.patch:
    libcxx atomic tests for old i386 fail with wrong Atomic inline width.
    Needed for libc++
    (See https://llvm.org/bugs/show_bug.cgi?id=19355)
